com.netease.stream.client

类 StreamClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netease.stream.client.DefaultClient
      • com.netease.stream.client.StreamClient
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Stream

    public class StreamClient
extends DefaultClient
implements Stream
    The client for accessing the Netease streamproxy service. The client provides storage service on the Internet. This client can be used to store and retrieve any amount of data, at any time, from anywhere on client.

      • StreamClient

        public StreamClient(String accessKey,
                    String secretKey)
        Constructs a new streamproxy client using the specified credentials and client configuration to access streamproxy.
        参数:
        accessKey - The access id to use when making requests to streamproxy with this client.
        secretKey - The secret key to use when making requests to streamproxy with this client.

                                                    String subscriptionName,
                                                    String resourcePath)
        Creates and initializes a subscription position request object for the specified streamproxy resource. This method is responsible for determining the right way to address resources. Callers can take the request, add any additional headers or parameters, then sign and execute the request.
        参数:
        positionType - wanted log position type.
        subscriptionName - subscription logs name.
        resourcePath - resource path,which to visit.
        返回:

      • shutdown

        public void shutdown()
        Shuts down this HTTP client object, releasing any resources that might be held open. This is an optional method, and callers are not expected to call it, but can if they want to explicitly release any open resources. Once a client has been shutdown, it cannot be used to make more requests.
        覆盖:
        shutdown 在类中 DefaultClient
